$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_in_editor

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_in_editor -  This method returns the value of the in editor flag.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_in_editor()
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
non-zero in editor, 0 not in an editor
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/line_ed.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the value of the in editor flag.
It will return non-zero if the player is in an editor.
.EP

